social_posts.post_text:
I loved exploring Cusco with my @warriorretreats family in container two. After the experience of the jungles, I was blessed to get back to the pleasures of the modern world we take for granted (like air conditioning :-) Cusco is vibrant, beautiful and full of culture. We had amazing meals @yakuperuvianrestaurant @greenpointcusco @cicciolinacusco visited ancient Inca cities, experienced the most passionate cooking class @marcelobatatacusco and were overwhelmed at the greatest amount of joy from giving back. 

#cusco #perú #travel

Hello and Dubai. 🫶🏻
Congrats to the @linglingdubai team on an incredible opening weekend! @atlantistheroyal is truly a phenomenal resort, thank you to everyone who helped make this weekend so special.

I just wanted to say HI. 
📸: @spiribolt
#machupicchu was a challenge, but also pure magic. The vibration was high with my @warriorretreats squad!
New Yo Show with @mikesnedegar, celebrity relations for Tao Group. We’re talking Madonna, Kardashians, DJ Khaled and the inner workings of #Vegas nightlife! Watch more on YouTube / Facebook.

Went to Israel with friends and had the time of my life. 
Thank you @tallywood for putting together such an epic adventure, including us all, and pushing me to book my flights. Can’t wait until next year. 😎⚡️❤️👑
